 {"id":"bd-1uog","title":"E2E tests: setup UI install flow + manifest ordering","description":"Goal:\n- Add Playwright tests for setup UI flows driven by manifest phases/tags.\n\nScope:\n- Required vs optional tool grouping; phase ordering.\n- Install action triggers correct API calls.\n- Detailed logs (network traces + DOM snapshots).\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- E2E tests pass and produce diagnostic logs.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:48:55.923798166Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T06:39:53.410223379Z","closed_at":"2026-01-27T06:39:53.410138630Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","setup","tests","web"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1uog","depends_on_id":"bd-1hac","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:48:55.984715237Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-1uog","depends_on_id":"bd-2xku","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:49:14.156587939Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
